OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776874270
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty after arson
OL,4,Cattack on synagogue in north-west
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FA 17-year-old boy has pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto arson after an attack on a
OL,9,Fsynagogue in north-west London.
OL,11,FThe teenager, a British national from
OL,12,FBrent, north-west London, who has not
OL,13,Fbeen named because of his age,
OL,14,Fadmitted arson not endangering life at
OL,15,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FTuesday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
