CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776874270
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty after arson
OL,4,Cattack on synagogue in north-west
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FFootage was posted online appearing to
OL,8,Fshow a figure in dark clothing setting
OL,9,Flight to a bottle of liquid and
OL,10,Fthrowing it through a window at Kenton
OL,11,FUnited Synagogue in Harrow late on
OL,12,FSaturday.
OL,14,FJewish charity the Community Security
OL,15,FTrust said minor smoke damage to an
OL,16,Finternal room was caused but there
OL,17,Fwere no injuries or significant
OL,18,Fstructural damage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
