OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776874270
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty after arson
OL,4,Cattack on synagogue in north-west
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FAt the short hearing, the 17-year-old,
OL,8,Fwho was flanked by two security
OL,9,Fofficers in the dock, spoke only to
OL,10,Fconfirm his personal details and to
OL,11,Fplead guilty to the charge.
OL,13,FTwo family members, including his
OL,14,Fmother, sat in seats in front of the
OL,15,Fdock.
OL,17,FTwo other suspects are "outstanding"
OL,18,Fin the investigation, the court heard.
OL,26,@yD@XOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
