CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1776874270
OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty after arson
OL,4,Cattack on synagogue in north-west
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FDistrict Judge Nina Tempia freed the
OL,8,Fyouth on bail with conditions
OL,9,Fincluding to live and sleep at his
OL,10,Fhome address and to not enter any
OL,11,Fsynagogue.
OL,13,FShe told the defendant: "I'm going to
OL,14,Fgrant you bail so that you can be
OL,15,Freleased today.
OL,17,F"If you breach these bail conditions
OL,18,Fyou will be arrested by the police."
OL,20,FThe boy is due to appear at Willesden
OL,21,FYouth Court on June 4.
OL,26,@uD@YOUyD@AOUzD@dO]
