OL,3,CTeenager pleads guilty after arson
OL,4,Cattack on synagogue in north-west
OL,5,CLondon
OL,7,FA 19-year-old man who was also
OL,8,Farrested after the attack has been
OL,9,Freleased on bail pending further
OL,10,Finquiries, the Metropolitan Police
OL,11,Fsaid.
